                <h4>2. Entering Games</h4>
                <p><span>2.1 Win &amp; Win Products and Services will be available through the Platform for AED 40 (forty Dirhams) each, or such other amount as We may determine from time to time.</span></p>
                <p><span>2.2 Each purchased Win &amp; Win Product and Service provides You with one complimentary Entry to the Draw.</span></p>
                <p><span>2.3 You may only enter the Draw if You:</span></p>
                <p><span>a) are at least 18 years of age at the time of purchase.</span></p>
                <p><span>b) are not prohibited or restricted from entering under the laws of Your jurisdiction of residence or jurisdiction in which You are located when entering.</span></p>
                <p><span>c) abide by these Rules and the Terms &amp; Conditions and Privacy Policy.</span></p>
                <p><span>d) are not:</span></p>
                <ul type="disc">
                   <li><span>a manager, employee, or an Immediate Family Member of Win &amp; Win.</span></li>
                   <li><span>a manager or employee of an affiliated company.</span></li>
                   <li><span>the Government Representative, the Insurance Representative, or the Draw Manager.</span></li>
                   <li><span>a third party, contractor, or consultant of the Manager engaged to review the insurance, audit, and security procedures related to the Draw.</span></li>
                   <li><span>a resident of a sanctioned or embargoed country; or</span></li>
                   <li><span>named on a Sanctions List</span></li>
                </ul>
                <p><span>2.4 Where You purchase a Win &amp; Win Product and Service online via the Win &amp; Win Website or Mobile App, upon purchase of the Win &amp; Win Pen, You will, after completion of the purchase, be asked to select a six-digit number, like a previously saved Favourite number or use the Quick Pick option.</span></p>
                <p><span>2.5 Any “credits” held in the Wallet Balance can only be used to enter the Game(s). Credits cannot be refunded due to financial regulations within the UAE.</span></p>
                <p><span>2.6 All successful Entries will be acknowledged via email, in-Platform messages, and, where relevant, a push notification.</span></p>
                <p><span>2.7 If You do not receive an acknowledgment of Your Entry, this may not have been recorded on the Central Computer System for the relevant Draw, and therefore, it may not be valid. If you do not receive an acknowledgment, please check Your Account to see if Your Entry has been registered. If You cannot see it, please contact Win &amp; Win Customer Service Centre at 800 xx-xxx-xxx in the UAE or +971 x xxx-XXXX for all other locations or by email at&nbsp;</span><u><span>info@winandwin.ae</span></u><span>.</span></p>
                <p><span>2.8 Entries made on the day of the relevant Draw after 8:30 pm (Gulf Standard Time), or such other time or day as We may determine, will not be entered into that Draw but will be entered in the next Draw.</span></p>
                <p><span>2.9 There is no general right for a customer to enter a Draw. We may refuse Entries and limit the number of Entries you can make without giving a reason.</span></p>
                <h4>3. Draw</h4>
                <p><span>3.1 We will determine the Draw’s time, frequency, date, and method. As of these Rules, the Raffle and Ball Draw will be held at approximately 9 pm (Gulf Standard Time) each Sunday. This timing may vary at certain times of year (i.e., Ramadan) or for special occasions.</span></p>
                <p><span>3.2 Each Draw will be made using an internationally certified Random Number Generator and a Ball Draw Machine, which will be audited at the time of the Draw.</span></p>
                <p><span>3.3 All Draws will be conducted per the Win &amp; Win Draw Procedures and in the presence of the Draw Manager, an Insurance Representative, and Government Representative. The Draw Manager and the Insurance Representative or Government Representative will record in writing and, subsequently, enter the Winning Numbers in the Central Computer System. Only these numbers will be the Winning Numbers for that Draw.</span></p>
                <p><span>3.4 If any Draw is declared invalid by the Draw Procedures, another Draw will be conducted to determine the Winning Numbers.</span></p>
                <p><span>3.5 If a Draw does not occur or is interrupted due to equipment failure or other reasons, the Draw will be completed by the Draw Procedures.</span></p>
                <h4>4. Results</h4>
                <p><span>4.1 All winnings from the Raffle and Ball Draw will be transferred to the Customer’s Winning Balance.</span></p>
                <p><span>4.2 The Winning Numbers for each Draw will be made available on the Platform and through Win &amp; Win Customer Service Centre as soon as practicable after each Draw. The Winning Numbers may be published as We may determine from time to time. You will have no claim for compensation for any failure on Our part to publicize the Winning Numbers or for failure to notify holders of winning Entries.</span></p>
                <p><span>4.3 You will not be entitled to claim compensation. We will not be bound by any errors contained in any announcement or publication, whether typographical, printing, or otherwise, or any publication or information of the amount of the Prizes in a Draw (where the information or publication is made before the amount to be paid in Prizes is finalized).</span></p>
                <p><span>4.4 In the event of a discrepancy between the Winning Numbers published on the Platform and other announcements or publications and the official Winning Numbers contained on the Central Computer System, the latter shall prevail.</span></p>
                <p><span>4.5 If the final verified number of winning Entries is different than the initial publicized number of provisional winning Entries, the Prize money payable to such winners may vary.</span></p>
                <h4>5. Winning a Prize</h4>
                <p><span>5.1 Raffle Draw</span></p>
                <p><span>a) There is one Prize category for each Draw.</span></p>
                <p><span>b) For all entries in the Raffle Draw, the Number Selection will be automatically picked by an internationally certified RNG.</span></p>
                <p><span>c) Each of the seven (6) winners will receive AED 44,444.</span></p>
